1268
00:52:37,387 --> 00:52:40,824
-Like dried seafood?
-He's pulling out the moisture.

1269
00:52:40,891 --> 00:52:42,726
-Like half-dried seafood?
-Yes.

1270
00:52:42,792 --> 00:52:45,695
Is it like dried bean curd,
like the ones you find in <i>malatang</i>?

1271
00:52:45,762 --> 00:52:47,497
This will create a chewy texture.

1272
00:52:47,564 --> 00:52:49,900
Nam-no, have you ever done this before?

1273
00:52:49,966 --> 00:52:51,735
I mean, in a pan?

1274
00:52:51,801 --> 00:52:53,236
-What? Yes.
-Have you done it?

1275
00:52:53,303 --> 00:52:54,838
No. This is…

1276
00:52:56,173 --> 00:52:59,543
