-It's burnt.

1379
00:56:46,803 --> 00:56:49,906
-Chef Nam-no also adds comical relief.
-He does.

1380
00:56:49,973 --> 00:56:52,776
-He does that.
-He's the comedic chef.

1381
00:56:53,910 --> 00:56:55,979
I CAN'T BE A COMEDIC CHEF
JUST LIKE THIS

