00:56:58,081 --> 00:57:01,317
THE TOP-NOTCH CHEF'S
EXCELLENT CHOPPING SKILLS!

1383
00:57:01,384 --> 00:57:02,719
AMAZED

1384
00:57:02,786 --> 00:57:05,188
Chef Nam-no has
amazing skills with his knife.

1385
00:57:06,589 --> 00:57:09,459
POONG ALSO FIGHTS BACK
