00:57:19,068 --> 00:57:21,871
Chef Nam-no also uses cherry tomatoes
just like Chef Fabri.

1391
00:57:21,938 --> 00:57:24,340
-I see.
-Cherry tomatoes are playing a big part.

1392
00:57:24,407 --> 00:57:27,277
Fabri had a great result
after using cherry tomatoes.

1393
00:57:27,343 --> 00:57:28,545
He's using those too.

1394
00:57:28,611 --> 00:57:30,713
